data.description: Move in Ready! Come & see this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home on a large corner lot. Many new or recently updated features to include new water heater, window blinds, screen doors, light fixtures, faucets, shower heads, garbage disposal and fresh paint on 2022. This large home provides dual stair access! Nice kitchen w/ breakfast area & bay window, peninsula bar, S/S appliances & tile floor. Upon entering the house there is a living room to the left (would make a great office) & dining room to the right. Both the kitchen and family room have plantation shutters & the family room has a gas fireplace flanked on each side with built-in shelves.  Large master bedroom w/ a walk-in closet. Gorgeous & spacious deck in the backyard w/ privacy fenced which is good for entertaining. Home is located minutes away from highways, Mall, restaurants & shopping centers. Convenient to Military bases.
